

################### Web services #############################

Install the pip package installer and other command-line tools by running the following commands:

sudo apt update

sudo apt install --yes python3-pip ruby-foreman httpie sqlite3

Use the python3 command to run Python and pip from the terminal.

Install Bottle and the Bottle-Sqlite plugin by running the following command:

python3 -m pip install bottle bottle-sqlite



################### Web app #################################

sudo apt install nodejs npm

npm install -g express-generator

express --view=pug  web-app
